Class AConversionProvider

java.lang.Object
com.tagnumelite.projecteintegration.api.conversion.AConversionProvider
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlexCavesAddon.ATMConversionProvider, AllTheModiumAddon.ATMConversionProvider, AppliedEnergisticsAddon.AEConversionProvider, ArsNouveauAddon.ANConversionProvider, BloodMagicAddon.BloodMagicConversion, ElementalCraftAddon.ECConversionProvider, EvilCraftAddon.ECConversionProvider, FarmersDelightAddon.FDConversionProvider, ImmersiveEngineeringAddon.IEConversionProvider, IndustrialForegoingAddon.IFConversionProvider, ManaAndArtificeAddon.MAAConversionProvider, MysticalAgricultureAddon.MysticalAgricultureConversionProvider, NaturesAuraAddon.NAConversionProvider
public abstract class AConversionProvider extends Object
An abstract class for generating custom conversions for ProjectE. Use ConversionProvider to denote your class as a conversion provider. There are a few utility functions for getting NormalizedSimpleStack from tags.
